      full parameter constructor.
      Parameters:
      axis - description of the time axis.
      timesys - time scale for the time coordinates.
      trefpos - reference position for the time coordinates.
      mjdref - base time offset; time coordinate values are relative to this.
      exposure - duration in time that the instrument was collecting data.
      resolution - smallest separation in time that can be distinguished.
